{
  "stem": "16214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that's-- that was something very dear to my heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the times I was called by the Psychiatry Department if I could come and help them, because I spoke Polish and Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there is a young woman in the psychiatric ward who tried to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she speaks only Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went there, and I found out after a little while, I was coming to visit her several days before I got to hear what she had to say.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the reasons for her trying to commit suicide was that she was only told some months ago, before the-- the trial of the suicide, that she was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened was she was living in Krakow-- she was living in Krakow, and going to Krakow University.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was one of the foremost leaders of antisemetic outbreaks in Krakow University at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] basically going after all the Jews who were the students.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was, you know, causing some really bad riots there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she was caught by the police finally, and put into a prison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And while being in prison, a person or two people, actually, from the Israeli embassy came to visit her, just to tell her that they discovered that she's a child of someone who is looking for her in Israel.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And basically, you know, they told her she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had, you know, she could do either of these two, either not to go, decide to stay away, you know, and-- or just decide to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
